Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀錄下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑雷米亞．哥特瓦爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶給你敗北的 有紀念意義的男人之名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀念? 那和我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我沒有記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動起來 Tristan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只能飛也好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下輻射波動也用盡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護盾能量也耗完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏不了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連GEASS的詛咒都用上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮 如此強大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是這邊的規格比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 有這樣的力量 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束吧 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果有正義的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 沒打到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你打到了 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你贏了 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經在靠自己的意志活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也能走自己的路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用了吧 GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑劣 無恥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…太過分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛者樞木朱雀已敗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無意求生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了那位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂耶 你最近才得知魯魯修的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻理解他的一部分本質
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是神聖布里塔尼亞帝國皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修．V．布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 魯魯修使用了Freyja代表…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修奈澤爾已加入我麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至此 Damocles與Freyja也全部為我所用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑騎士團不再擁有與我對抗的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也要垂死掙扎的話 招待你們的只會是Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無人能阻我霸業
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 今天這一瞬間 世界已陷落我手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修．V．布里塔尼亞下令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界啊 臣服於我吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Lelouch!




Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神聖布里塔尼亞帝國第99代唯一皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼黑騎士團C.E.O. 超合眾國第2代最高評議會議長

Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修．V．布里塔尼亞陛下出現在我們眼前



Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反對魯魯修陛下的愚昧之徒 正被送往刑場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次大戰中 帝都Pendragon和眾多將士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括Knight of Zero樞木朱雀卿在內 付出了慘重的犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E.U.批准超合眾國憲章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的魯魯修陛下 終於實現了世界統一偉業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光榮與魯魯修陛下同在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單純的獨裁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗者全部被殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓 被人聽到的話會滿門抄斬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不得不把這種內容作為正義報導
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修 這就是你想做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配世界和人們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時何必與魯魯修頂嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為迎來明天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算重複著成功與失敗也必須前行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人和科學是一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是進化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是進步 布丁伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在記恨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅伊德先生和拉克夏塔以前發生過什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是些瑣碎的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想想根本不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在出去正中他們下懷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 魯魯修在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道魯魯修他們策劃的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開槍 我來對付他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 假面騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 按約定你來殺死我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:16:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按預定 世界的仇很正集中在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我消失 就能斬斷這仇恨的鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑騎士團留有ZERO的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修奈澤爾也會聽命於ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣世界將不再用軍事力量 而是在談判桌上就能解決
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能朝明天前進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零之鎮魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在C的世界中 我們明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們期望著明天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得願望和GEASS很像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠自己無法實現的事會尋求他人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:17:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就對所有人使用名為願望的GEASS


Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了世界的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修 你作為對人使用GEASS的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被殺的覺悟 才有資格開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 你要成為英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從世界的敵人

Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝魯魯修．V．布里塔尼亞手中拯救世界的救世主



Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯…魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對你來說也是懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:18:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須作為正義的使者戴著面具活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再是樞木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也必須為世界犧牲常人該有的幸福 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份GEASS 我確實收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…哥哥之前都是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我愛你

Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…毀滅世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造…世界…



Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜開眼睛 哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王魯魯修已死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放人質
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫且撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道那是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍賴 我有哥哥就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:20:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哥哥的明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後世界好了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:21:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用在戰爭上的能源 現在用在饑餓與貧困
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種仇恨與罪名都被被你一手包辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家比起Damocles這個系統 更容易記住一個有名有姓的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠可笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 正因為如此 大家才不會被過去束縛 能繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又會笑著說「如我所料」了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然還留下了各種問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為GEASS的王的力量 會令人孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像不太對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 魯魯修